sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Management Client
    participant RESTCONF as RESTCONF API
    participant Yang as YANG Models
    participant SMF as SMF
    participant DB as Database

    Client->>RESTCONF: HTTP GET /restconf/data/network-functions
    RESTCONF->>Yang: Validate Request
    RESTCONF->>DB: Retrieve Data
    DB-->>RESTCONF: Network Functions Data
    RESTCONF-->>Client: JSON Response
    
    Client->>RESTCONF: HTTP POST /restconf/data/network-functions/amf
    Note over Client,RESTCONF: Create New AMF
    RESTCONF->>Yang: Validate Payload
    RESTCONF->>DB: Store New AMF
    DB-->>RESTCONF: Confirmation
    RESTCONF->>SMF: Notify Configuration Change
    SMF-->>RESTCONF: Acknowledgment
    RESTCONF-->>Client: JSON Response (201 Created)
    
    Client->>RESTCONF: HTTP PUT /restconf/data/network-functions/amf/amf-001
    Note over Client,RESTCONF: Update Existing AMF
    RESTCONF->>Yang: Validate Payload
    RESTCONF->>DB: Update AMF
    DB-->>RESTCONF: Confirmation
    RESTCONF->>SMF: Apply Configuration
    SMF-->>RESTCONF: Acknowledgment
    RESTCONF-->>Client: JSON Response
    
    Client->>RESTCONF: HTTP DELETE /restconf/data/network-functions/amf/amf-001
    RESTCONF->>DB: Remove AMF
    DB-->>RESTCONF: Confirmation
    RESTCONF->>SMF: Notify Removal
    SMF-->>RESTCONF: Acknowledgment
    RESTCONF-->>Client: HTTP 204 No Content

